From thomas.friedrichsmeier@ruhr-uni-bochum.de  Sun Nov 17 13:53:38 2002
From: thomas.friedrichsmeier@ruhr-uni-bochum.de (thomas)
Date: Sun, 17 Nov 2002 14:53:38 +0100
Subject: [R-gui] Another R-GUI
In-Reply-To: <MABBLJDICACNFOLGIHJOEENPDAAA.phgrosje@ulb.ac.be>
