From thomas.friedrichsmeier@ruhr-uni-bochum.de  Thu Nov 28 17:25:51 2002
From: thomas.friedrichsmeier@ruhr-uni-bochum.de (thomas.friedrichsmeier@ruhr-uni-bochum.de)
